reviewText: It IS a nice CD, if You are a fan You will Like IT

I went to the live taping of this show almost a year ago. It was one of those moments in life that I will never forget. Having bought the DVD and watching it, made me re-live those special moments. His voice is divine. And the guest singers were amazing as well. It is definitely a show everyone must see. You will be singing and dancing in front of your TV the whole time. Cristian is definitely a Mexican icon of our time. He's by far one of the best singers ever!
